name: にちか
text:
あーはいお疲れ様でしたー、すぐ着替えるんで
話しかけないでもらっていいですかねー……
trans:
Yeah yeah, thanks for your support.
I need to get changed immediately so I'd appreciate
it if you didn't speak to me right now.

name: プロデューサー
text: ────いろんなこと、確かめるための機会だったんだ
trans:
────This rehearsal was just about figuring out
what you still need to work on.

name: にちか
text: …………ないので、焦ってる感じですねー
trans:
...Actually, there really isn't, and that's why I'm
panicking.

name: にちか
text: 全然全然、全然…………ぜんっぜん全然──────
trans:
I'm nowhere, nowhere... nowhere, not anywhere
even close to being ready────

name: にちか
text: 何しに来たのって思ってると思います、先生も…………！
trans:
Everyone watching that rehearsal had to be
thinking, "What is she even doing here?", even
the instructors...!

name: にちか
text:
せっかくの、美琴さんの…………
…………絶対に、絶対に絶対に汚せないので────
trans:
I could never ever ever forgive myself...
If I tarnished Mikoto's first performance in
so long────

name: にちか
text:
────着替えてきます。着替えて現場行って現場行って
練習して練習して…………
trans:
────I'm going to go get changed. I'll get changed,
and go to my next job, then the job after that, then
go to practice, and then do more practice...
